{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-jsx","path":"/20201121-fontawesome-scroll-to-top/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"rrih"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"2b418eb5-f1ab-5c3c-8b9d-e95fb708c258","excerpt":"深夜に寝る前に思いつきで追加したのでてきとうすぎです。 手順 先に必要なパッケージをインストールしておく あとは layout.js に書くだけ。 ちなみに react-fontawesome で使用する場合、camel case…","html":"<p>深夜に寝る前に思いつきで追加したのでてきとうすぎです。</p>\n<h4>手順</h4>\n<p>先に必要なパッケージをインストールしておく</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> i react-scroll\n$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> i --save @fortawesome/fontawesome-svg-core @fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons @fortawesome/react-fontawesome</code></pre></div>\n<p>あとは layout.js に書くだけ。</p>\n<p>ちなみに react-fontawesome で使用する場合、camel case で読み込みます。<br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">fa-arrow-up</code>の場合、<code class=\"language-text\">faArrowUp</code>で読み込むことができます。</p>\n<p>具体的には</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> animateScroll <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> scroll <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react-scroll'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> FontAwesomeIcon <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@fortawesome/react-fontawesome'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> faArrowUp <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons'</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>FontAwesomeIcon icon<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>faArrowUp<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> onClick<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>scroll<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">scrollToTop</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>このような感じ。</p>\n<p>当サイトの該当コードは<a href=\"https://github.com/rrih/rrih.github.io/blob/master/src/components/layout.js#L87\">こちら</a></p>\n<h4>参考文献</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://qiita.com/takk0715/items/6b82d7b4d13134d717eb\">React-Scroll で smooth なスクロールを実装してみた。 - Qiita</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.corylog.com/gatsby/gatsby014/\">GatsbyJS で fontawesome を使う | コリログ</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>関連記事</h4>\n<p><a href=\"/20201123-fontawesome-perfect-understand\">react-fontawesome(fas, far, fab)</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"react-fontawesome+react-scrollでページトップへスクロールするやつを追加した","date":"2020年11月21日","description":"","tags":["react","fontawesome"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/20201121-fontawesome-scroll-to-top/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/20201120-where-todo/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"結局TODOリストって何に書けばいいんだろうね","tags":["雑記"]}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/20201122-kimetsu-no-yaiba-movie/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"鬼滅の刃 無限列車編を観た感想","tags":["雑記"]}}}}}